Fieldname,DataType,Description
,_TITLE_,Target status
TARGET,String,The name of the target that the row applies to
PERIODS,Integer,The number of periods in the simulation
ACTIVE,Boolean,The active status of the target
MINACTIVE,Boolean,The active status of the minimum target
MAXACTIVE,Boolean,The active status of the maximum target
DISCOUNT,Number,The discount rate applied to this target
LINEAR,Boolean,Flag for linear scaling
PREMULTIPLY,Boolean,Flag for premultiplication of weight values
